
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tips</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/content.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/layout.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>
    <section class="travel-tips">
        <div class="tips-header">
          <h2>Travel Tips</h2>
          <p>Make your journey smoother and more memorable with our essential tips!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tips-grid">
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>Pack Smart</h3>
            <p>Use packing cubes and make a checklist to avoid overpacking.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>Stay Flexible</h3>
            <p>Always allow extra time in your itinerary for unexpected adventures.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>Local Research</h3>
            <p>Learn a few local phrases and customs to connect better with locals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>Health First</h3>
            <p>Carry basic medicines and stay hydrated, especially on long flights.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>Backup Documents</h3>
            <p>Keep digital copies of important documents like passport and visa.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>Budget Wisely</h3>
            <p>Set daily spending limits to manage your money and avoid surprises.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
      
</body>
</html>
